            "Skillcheck",       -- Prioritas 1: Segala jenis kartu Speed (Movement Speed)
            "Stamina",          -- Prioritas 2: Segala jenis kartu Stamina
            "Stealth",          -- Prioritas 3: Bonus Skillcheck / Ichor Extraction
            "Speed",            -- Prioritas 4: Kartu Stealth / Anti ketahuan
